{"type": "article", "id": 16968, "title": "沙子钟", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-03T06:00:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607114957HLZSJKtViyk3sl16.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是一面沙子钟，它只有一根时针，一面勾出了涟漪纹路，另一面将它抚平。当这面钟是完整的涟漪纹路时指向了中午 12 点，完全平整则是 0 点，每转一圈相当于 12 个小时。设计的灵感源于日本园林中有涟漪纹路的沙子装饰，有一种静谧的美学意境。它可能没有那么精准，却像沙漏一样揭示了时间的短暂和滑过无痕。</span><a href=\"http://www.ayaskan.com/work/sand/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144207V3soMlTUiqnKIEx1.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144208PqRgtduUvmzlBf9T.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"805\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.89444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144208uBFr5AMd9k6XJKbW.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"294\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144209bgRxHVkJfrvI68eF.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}